extends com.guidewire.pl.persistence.code.BeanBase
implements Editable, AggregateLimitRptDelegate
    AggregateLimitRpt Represents denormalized aggregate limit used calculations (i.e., the amount of the limit that has been used to date) for a PolicyPeriod and, optionally, a coverageline.
